edu.stanford.nlp.international.spanish

Class SpanishUnknownWordSignatures

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.stanford.nlp.international.spanish.SpanishUnknownWordSignatures

  • public class SpanishUnknownWordSignatures
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains patterns for matching certain word types in Spanish, such as common suffices for nouns, verbs, adjectives and adverbs. These utilities are used to characterize unknown words within the POS tagger and the parser.
    Author:
    Jon Gauthier
    See Also:
    ExtractorFramesRare, SpanishUnknownWordModel
